title: Royals rout Blue Jays 14-2, 1 win from World Series return
text:
> Top News Royals rout Blue Jays 14-2, 1 win from World Series return Kansas City Royals' Ben Zobrist (18) celebrates his two-run home run with teammate Eric Hosmer (35) during the first inning in Game 4 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, in Toronto. (Nathan Denette/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
